  multiline systems, this should sort the problem out.
  Thanks to Fredrik Berstrom

- Three versions.
  MaxRexx.000 - 68000, 010, 020, 030, 040, 060
  MaxRexx.020 - 020, 030, 040, 060
  MaxRexx.040 - 040, 060


